          -  Lower risk of anastomotic leakage

          -  Advanced neoplasia (T4)

          -  Indication for inter-sphincteric resection hydro-pneumatic test of the anastomosis
             tightness showed positive for air leak

          -  Surgical procedure intraoperatively modified from the standard laparoscopic anterior
             rectal resection
      </textblock>
